PackageManagerService
=====================

## PMS启动流程

```java
// == system_server ==
// frameworks\base\services\java\com\android\server\SystemServer.java
    private void startBootstrapServices() {
        PackageManagerService.main(... installer, ...)
    }

// frameworks\base\services\core\java\com\android\server\pm\PackageManagerService.java
    public static PackageManagerService main(Context context, Installer installer, boolean factoryTest, boolean onlyCore) {
        // 创建PackageManagerService对象
        PackageManagerService m = new PackageManagerService(context, installer,factoryTest, onlyCore);
        ServiceManager.addService("package", m);

        final PackageManagerNative pmn = m.new PackageManagerNative();
        ServiceManager.addService("package_native", pmn);
    }

// 在PackageManagerService的构造函数中要完成很多工作，如扫描各个安装目录下的apk文件，解析，安装扫描到的apk应用
// 整个构造函数很长，根据eventlog，可以分成5个阶段
    public PackageManagerService(Context context, Installer installer, boolean factoryTest, boolean onlyCore) {
        // 1. BOOT_PROGRESS_PMS_START
        EventLog.writeEvent(EventLogTags.BOOT_PROGRESS_PMS_START, SystemClock.uptimeMillis());
        // 2. BOOT_PROGRESS_PMS_SYSTEM_SCAN_START
        EventLog.writeEvent(EventLogTags.BOOT_PROGRESS_PMS_SYSTEM_SCAN_START, startTime);
        // 3. BOOT_PROGRESS_PMS_DATA_SCAN_START
        EventLog.writeEvent(EventLogTags.BOOT_PROGRESS_PMS_DATA_SCAN_START, SystemClock.uptimeMillis());
        // 4. BOOT_PROGRESS_PMS_SCAN_END
        EventLog.writeEvent(EventLogTags.BOOT_PROGRESS_PMS_SCAN_END, SystemClock.uptimeMillis());
        // 5. BOOT_PROGRESS_PMS_READY
        EventLog.writeEvent(EventLogTags.BOOT_PROGRESS_PMS_READY, SystemClock.uptimeMillis());
    }
```

### BOOT_PROGRESS_PMS_START阶段

这个阶段主要任务是初始化`mSettings`对象，相关调用有：

```java
// 创建mSettings对象
mSettings = new Settings(Environment.getDataDirectory(), mPermissionManager.getPermissionSettings(), mPackages);

// 初始化android:sharedUserId配置，如果APP在AndroidManifest.xml中声明了android:sharedUserId，那么共享UID相关的权限配置在这里被初始化好
mSettings.addSharedUserLPw("android.uid.system", Process.SYSTEM_UID, ApplicationInfo.FLAG_SYSTEM, ApplicationInfo.PRIVATE_FLAG_PRIVILEGED);

// 解析/data/system/packages.xml文件，初始化mSettings中的mPackages对象，关于mPackages对象的解释如下：
//     /** Map from package name to settings */
//     final ArrayMap<String, PackageSetting> mPackages = new ArrayMap<>();
mFirstBoot = !mSettings.readLPw(sUserManager.getUsers(false));
```

### mSettings.readLPw

readLPw()主要是读取并解析/data/system下关于package的信息文件。主要涉及到被解析的文件有：

- packages.xml： `PMS`扫描完目标文件夹后会创建该文件。当系统进行程序安装、卸载和更新等操作时，均会更新该文件。该文件保存了系统中与 package 相关的一些信息。
- packages-backup.xml：packages.xml的备份文件。
- packages.list：描述系统中存在的所有非系统自带的 APK 的信息。当这些程序有变动时，`PMS`就会更新该文件。
- packages-stopped.xml：从系统自带的设置程序中进入应用程序页面，然后在选择强制停止（ForceStop）某个应用时，系统会将该应用的相关信息记录到此文件中。也就是该文件保存系统中被用户强制停止的 `Package` 的信息。

###
/frameworks/base/services/core/java/com/android/server/pm/PackageManagerService.java
```
    public static PackageManagerService main(Context context, Installer installer,
            boolean factoryTest, boolean onlyCore) {
        PackageManagerService m = new PackageManagerService(context, installer,
                factoryTest, onlyCore);
        ServiceManager.addService("package", m);
        return m;
    }
```
这步执行后，就可以通过ServiceManager来获取PackageManagerService的binder proxy了

####
Settings构造函数

/frameworks/base/services/core/java/com/android/server/pm/Settings.java
```
    Settings(File dataDir, Object lock) {
        ...
        mSystemDir = new File(dataDir, "system");
        ...
        mSettingsFilename = new File(mSystemDir, "packages.xml");
        mBackupSettingsFilename = new File(mSystemDir, "packages-backup.xml");
        mPackageListFilename = new File(mSystemDir, "packages.list");
        ...
        // Deprecated: Needed for migration
        mStoppedPackagesFilename = new File(mSystemDir, "packages-stopped.xml");
        mBackupStoppedPackagesFilename = new File(mSystemDir, "packages-stopped-backup.xml");
    }
```
settings初始化过程中创建了一些xml文件：
1. packages.xml/packages-backup.xml:    记录系统中所有安装的应用的信息
2. packages-stopped.xml/packages-stopped-backup.xml:    被强制停止运行的应用信息
3. packages.list:   保存普通应用的数据目录和uid信息等

####
SystemConfig构造函数
```
    SystemConfig() {
        // Read configuration from system
        readPermissions(Environment.buildPath(
                Environment.getRootDirectory(), "etc", "sysconfig"), ALLOW_ALL);
        // Read configuration from the old permissions dir
        readPermissions(Environment.buildPath(
                Environment.getRootDirectory(), "etc", "permissions"), ALLOW_ALL);
        // Allow ODM to customize system configs around libs, features and apps
        readPermissions(Environment.buildPath(
                Environment.getOdmDirectory(), "etc", "sysconfig"), odmPermissionFlag);
        readPermissions(Environment.buildPath(
                Environment.getOdmDirectory(), "etc", "permissions"), odmPermissionFlag);
        // Only allow OEM to customize features
        readPermissions(Environment.buildPath(
                Environment.getOemDirectory(), "etc", "sysconfig"), ALLOW_FEATURES);
        readPermissions(Environment.buildPath(
                Environment.getOemDirectory(), "etc", "permissions"), ALLOW_FEATURES);
    }
```

构造函数中会操作etc目录下的配置文件，该对象会保存etc目录下的配置信息

        // (Do this before scanning any apps.)

```cpp
public static List<File> getFileList(String strPath) {
    File dir = new File(strPath);
    File[] files = dir.listFiles(); // 该文件目录下文件全部放入数组
    if (files != null) {
        for (int i = 0; i < files.length; i++) {
            String fileName = files[i].getName();
            if (files[i].isDirectory()) { // 判断是文件还是文件夹
                getFileList(files[i].getAbsolutePath()); // 获取文件绝对路径
            } else if (fileName.endsWith("avi")) { // 判断文件名是否以.avi结尾
                String strFileName = files[i].getAbsolutePath();
                System.out.println("---" + strFileName);
                filelist.add(files[i]);
            } else {
                continue;
            }
        }
    }
    return filelist;
}
```
